IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
User alexlibman97@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass email/alexlibman97@gmail.com"

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
